link_desc:
This is a modified version of the template found https://share.zabbix.com/printers/hp/hp-officejet-pro-8xxx altered to support Officejet 7000 series printers.

Linked to SNMP Generic and SNMP Interfaces to expand the useful data.

Graph included for supply levels.

Trigger for supply levels set to "Information" severity level.

Triggers supply value being 0 ~ 100.

Tested on HP Officejet Pro 7740.
author: Joseph Crowell
